<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Pow is installed</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #e0e0d8;
      line-height: 18px;
    }
    div.page {
      margin: 72px auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      -webkit-box-shadow: 0px 2px 7px #999;
      -moz-box-shadow: 0px 2px 7px #999;
      padding: 36px 90px;
      width: 480px;
      position: relative;
    }
    h1, h2, p, li {
      font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    h1 {
      line-height: 45px;
      font-size: 36px;
      color: #060;
      margin: 0;
    }
    h1:before {
      content: "âœ“";
      font-size: 66px;
      line-height: 42px;
      color: #090;
      position: absolute;
      right: 576px;
    }
    h2 {
      line-height: 27px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: normal;
      margin: 0;
    }
    a, pre span {
      color: #776;
    }
    h2, p, pre {
      color: #222;
    }
    ul {
      padding: 0;
    }
    li {
      list-style-type: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <h1>Pow is installed.</h1>
    <h2>You&rsquo;re running version <%= @version %></h2>
    <section>
      <p>Set up a Rack application by symlinking it into your <code>~/.pow</code> directory. The name of the symlink determines the hostname you&rsquo;ll use to access the application.</p>
      <pre><span>$</span> cd ~/.pow
<span>$</span> ln -s /path/to/myapp
<span>$</span> open http://myapp.<%= @domain %>/</pre>
    </section>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="http://pow.cx/manual">Pow User&rsquo;s Manual</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/37signals/pow/wiki/Troubleshooting">Troubleshooting</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/37signals/pow/wiki/FAQ">Frequently Asked Questions</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/37signals/pow/issues">Issue Tracker</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
